<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-08-03T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-08-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="1700" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1700">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 817.812/93.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President of Nicaragua</gloss>
                                to the <gloss type="to">Minister of Nicaragua</gloss>.</hi><note n="10" xml:id="d1700fn10">Translation left at the Department by the
                                Minister on August 4, 1914.</note>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Translation.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Managua</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-08-03">
                                    <hi rend="italic">August 3, 1914</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Canal treaty which you sent me in your cable of to-day meets with my
                            entire approbation. Advise me when the treaty has been signed.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Diaz</hi></signed>.</closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>